<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please see </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">the below link which will prompt you to re-set your password and allow you to log into the Kingsbridge IR35 Status Review tool</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">:<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>https://kingsbridge.ir35.io/forgot-password<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">ensure you log in before completing a review to avoid being prompted to make payment</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you have any further queries, please feel free to give us a call on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> or reply by email.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
